dataDictionary.title: New Relic data dictionary
dataDictionary.intro: <0>This data dictionary lists and defines the <2>attributes</2> attached to New Relic events and other data objects (like Metric and Span data).</0>
dataDictionary.callout: <0>This dictionary does not contain data reported by Infrastructure integrations. To learn about that data, see the <2>integration documentation</2>.</0>
